org.opends.sdk.schema.matchingrules
Class CaseExactIA5SubstringMatchingRule

java.lang.Object
  org.opends.sdk.schema.matchingrules.CaseExactIA5SubstringMatchingRule
All Implemented Interfaces:
MatchingRuleImplementation
public class CaseExactIA5SubstringMatchingRule
extends Object

This class implements the caseExactIA5SubstringsMatch matching rule. This matching rule actually isn't defined in any official specification, but some directory vendors do provide an implementation using an OID from their own private namespace.
